Name:           gnome-online-accounts
Version:        3.46.0
Release:        0
Summary:        GNOME service to access online accounts
License:        LGPL-2.0-or-later
Group:          System/GUI/GNOME
URL:            https://wiki.gnome.org/Projects/GnomeOnlineAccounts
